Roche declines comment on Astra . Roche Holding AG declined comment on rumours that it was interested in buying Sweden ' s Astra AB . " Our answer is the same . We cannot comment on market rumours , " a Roche spokesman said . The Roche spokesman late on Wednesday declined comment on rumours circulating in London that it may be preparing for a hostile bid or a merger with Smithkline Beecham Plc . Roche is often mentioned as a possible suitor when takeover speculation focuses on a large pharmaceutical group . It was in the past rumoured to be a potential suitor for Zeneca Group Plc . - - Zurich Editorial + 41 1 631 7340 
